Path of program

Source: R/utils.R
doc_path.Rd

Path of program

Usage

doc_path(filename = NULL, path = NULL)

Arguments

filename

Name of output file

path

program path

Value

character string

Examples

# \donttest{
 doc_path(filename = "my_tbl.pdf", path = NULL)
#> [1] "/home/runner/work/_temp/759cf65e-5093-42bb-80b8-f02dc3e70b00"
# }
